data.description: North Lakeland POOL home available.  This 3/2 pool home features an open floor plan, split bedrooms with water views, granite countertops throughout, wood laminate flooring and dining nook.  The pool is screened in and there is a spacious lanai as well as a double car garage. The seller is offering a flooring allowance for the existing carpet.  Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants and zoned for Lake Gibson schools.
